text: Durbalara ahankariderake balabe, baram tomara'i to dibaratri cakranta kare amaderake nirdesa dite yena amara allahake na mani ebam tamra ansidara sabyasta kari tara yakhana sasti dekhabe, takhana manera anutapa mane'i rakhabe. Bastutah ami kapheradera galaya beri paraba. Tara se pratiphala'i peye thake ya tara karata.
